# Blog slug naming

- Use English kebab-case for blog post filenames (e.g. `summer-and-fishing.md`).
- The filename becomes the URL slug (`/blog/summer-and-fishing/`).
- Titles in frontmatter may be in Japanese; only the filename/slug is English.
